  <original-body>*What I did:*

I added the mimetype &quot;application/vnd.google-earth.kml+xml&quot; mapped to extension .kml, and created a view show.kml.builder

*What should happen:*

Requests to /show.kml should use the show.kml.builder view, with the response type set to &quot;application/vnd.google-earth.kml+xml&quot;

*What does happen:*

Requests to /show.kml do use the show.kml.builder view, but the response type is set to &quot;application/xml&quot;

I will look into the best way to fix this evening</original-body>
